of the shooting just to make it sensational and wanted to die 
because of poor health and psychological problems demirag was 
quoted as saying he thought he would be killed immediately by 
ozals security police 
according to turkish newspapers the gunman has been giving 
contradictory testimonies since he was arrested 
according to the istanbul daily hurriyet demirag said that he 
did not act alone but the report did not say which group he 
claimed to be working with or provide other details 
demirag had been a member of the youth organization of the 
defunct neofascist national movement party according to the 
reports the youth group is known as the gray wolves or the 
idealist clubs which were involved in a wave of terrorism that 
claimed 5000 lives in 197880 
mehmet ali agca the turkish gunman who shot and wounded pope 
