low level would stay closed for up to three days halting up to 
1800 barges 
that section of the river has shrunk from 500 feet wide and 15 
feet deep to 170 feet wide and nine feet deep he said the dredge 
was to dig it out to 12 feet to 14 feet deep and widen it to 300 
feet 
the freeing of a 26barge tow that ran aground near rosedale 
